<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Under Maintenance — PoGORaids</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;0,900;1,700&family=Barlow:wght@400;500;600&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --ink:       #08090f;
      --panel:     #10121c;
      --border:    rgba(80,140,255,0.12);
      --cyan:      #3be8ff;
      --cyan-dim:  #1ab8d4;
      --logo-grad: linear-gradient(135deg,#3be8ff 0%,#7b3fff 55%,#b020ff 100%);
      --text:      #e8eaf0;
      --muted:     #7a82a0;
      --font-head: 'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;
      --font-body: 'Barlow',sans-serif;
      --font-mono: 'Space Mono',monospace;
    }
    body { 
      background: var(--ink); 
      color: var(--text); 
      font-family: var(--font-body); 
      display: flex; 
      flex-direction: column; 
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    body::before {
      content:''; position:fixed; inset:0;
      background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(59,128,255,.04) 1px,transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(59,128,255,.04) 1px,transparent 1px);
      background-size:60px 60px; pointer-events:none; z-index:0;
    }

    /* ── NAVBAR ── */
    .navbar { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 0 40px; height: 64px; display: flex; align-items: center; background: rgba(8,9,15,.92); backdrop-filter: blur(16px); position: relative; z-index: 10; }
    .nav-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-title { font-family: var(--font-head); font-weight: 900; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; background: var(--logo-grad); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; }

    /* ── CONTENT ── */
    .maintenance-wrap {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .maintenance-wrap::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; width: 500px; height: 500px; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(123,63,255,.12) 0%, transparent 65%); pointer-events: none;
    }

    .icon-box {
      font-size: 64px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: var(--cyan);
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 15px rgba(59,232,255,0.4));
      animation: pulse 2s infinite ease-in-out;
    }
    @keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); } 50% { opacity: 0.7; transform: scale(0.95); } }

    .eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: .3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--cyan); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    h1 { font-family: var(--font-head); font-weight: 900; font-size: clamp(32px, 8vw, 64px); text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 0.9; margin-bottom: 20px; background: var(--logo-grad); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
    p { color: var(--muted); max-width: 480px; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; line-height: 1.6; }

    .btn-back {
      background: var(--logo-grad);
      color: #fff;
      font-family: var(--font-head);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15px;
      letter-spacing: .1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(123,63,255,0.4);
    }
    .btn-back:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(59,232,255,0.3); }

    .status-card {
      margin-top: 48px;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .status-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; background: #ffbc00; border-radius: 50%; box-shadow: 0 0 8px #ffbc00; }

    footer { padding: 24px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); position: relative; z-index: 10; }
    footer p { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav class="navbar">
    <a href="index.html" class="nav-logo">
      <span class="nav-title">PoGORaids</span>
    </a>
  </nav>

  <main class="maintenance-wrap">
    <div class="icon-box">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-screwdriver-wrench"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="eyebrow">// System Update</div>
    <h1>Under Construction</h1>
    <p>Our dev team is currently deploying new features to the Trainer Tools hub. We'll be back online shortly with improved raid coordination modules.</p>
    
    <a href="index.html" class="btn-back">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> Return to Base
    </a>

    <div class="status-card">
      <div class="status-dot"></div>
      STATUS: DEPLOYING_V2_MODULES
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2026 PoGORaids.net — Not affiliated with Niantic or Pokémon GO.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
